<section xml:id="AREAS" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude">
  <title>AREAS</title>

  <p> The area of a rectangle is found by: (base) x (height) </p>
  <p> The area of a triangle is found by: ½ (base) x (height) </p>
  <p> The area of a circle is found by: <m>π \times (\text{radius})^2</m>. </p>

</section>